EEG/RF Signal Research Provenance Chain
========================================
Pipeline:
  1. Acquire EEG/MMG signal (real device or simulation)
  2. Quantize signal → binary token sequence
  3. SHA-3 hash the binary → write to local append-only ledger
  4. Feed token sequence to DeepSeek LLM for analysis
  5. Hash the LLM analysis → also recorded on ledger

Provenance output:
  • ledger.jsonl  — append-only chain of blocks, each linking to previous
  • Each block contains: reading_hash, token_hash, llm_hash, timestamp, chain_hash
  • Verifiable offline — no external blockchain dependency required
  • Optional: anchor to Ethereum/Solana public chain via OP_RETURN or memo

Usage:
  python eeg_provenance_chain.py --mode cli
  python eeg_provenance_chain.py --mode server --ws-port 8765
  python eeg_provenance_chain.py --verify ledger.jsonl

Requirements:
  pip install openai numpy scipy rich
  pip install web3          # optional, for Ethereum anchoring
  pip install solana solders # optional, for Solana anchoring
"""

